HEADWORD: Blowfly
<hw>Blow"fly`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any species of fly of the genus <gen>Musca</gen> that deposits its
eggs or young larv⟦ae⟧ (called <xex>flyblows</xex> and
<xex>maggots</xex>) upon meat or other animal products.</def>⟦br⟧
